when you don't want to deal.

29:53.748 --> 29:55.445
I want to the funeral.

29:55.489 --> 29:56.925
I said good-bye.

29:56.969 --> 29:59.014
That doesn't mean
you've accepted anything.

29:59.058 --> 30:01.016
I'm fine.

30:01.060 --> 30:03.714
