developments at the hospital.

30:54.896 --> 30:58.987
I'd like to see them through,
because if things work out,

30:59.031 --> 31:02.121
let's just say you won't be
the only one with a new dynasty.

31:02.164 --> 31:04.645
Betting on yourself.
Can't argue with that.

31:04.688 --> 31:05.820
I know it's a risk.

31:05.864 --> 31:08.475
I really want to create
my own legacy.

31:08.518 --> 31:10.999
My last name can help
get me in the door,

31:11.043 --> 31:14.133
but I need to be able
to kick them down myself.

31:18.180 --> 31:22.619
And I would like for us
to work on

31:22.663 --> 31:24.839
building
a better relationship.

31:24.883 --> 31:26.536
I would like that, too.

31:26.580 --> 31:28.712
So you're not mad
that I said no?

31:28.756 --> 31:30.714
Not at all. No.

31:30.758 --> 31:32.238
Good luck.

31:37.199 --> 31:39.636
