would have done that?

31:45.991 --> 31:49.603
So, how much did you pay
the Hot Tea Atlantareporter

31:49.646 --> 31:51.735
to interview me?I didn't pay the reporter.

31:51.779 --> 31:54.869
So it was a coincidence
that you saw the show,

31:54.913 --> 31:57.219
and the reporter suddenly
took an interest

31:57.263 --> 31:58.829
in who I was wearing?

31:58.873 --> 32:01.049
It's true, I look stunning.

32:01.093 --> 32:03.486
But I wouldn't exactly say
I'm a Kardashian

32:03.530 --> 32:04.444
on the fame scale.

32:04.487 --> 32:07.055
I didn't pay the reporter.

32:07.099 --> 32:09.971
But I did buy the company.
You mad?

32:10.015 --> 32:14.715
Mad? You should see
our new sales projections.

32:14.758 --> 32:17.239
This feels like a move
out of my own playbook.

32:17.283 --> 32:20.155
Not sure if I should be
flattered or insulted.

32:20.199 --> 32:21.852
But you should have
told me the truth,

32:21.896 --> 32:23.680
just like you can tell me
what's bothering you now.

32:23.724 --> 32:26.596
Did you not hire
the scientist?
I did not.

32:26.640 --> 32:30.644
I don't get what's so important
about this man.

32:30.687 --> 32:32.907
There are a million ways for you

32:32.951 --> 32:34.517
to make your company
more efficient.

32:34.561 --> 32:35.997
That's not what this is about.

32:36.041 --> 32:37.651
Then what is it about?

32:39.783 --> 32:41.785
You want honesty?

32:41.829 --> 32:44.527
I had a vision on that retreat
a while back.

32:44.571 --> 32:47.182
I'm worried about this planet.

32:47.226 --> 32:51.534
So I want to build a rocket
and send it into space.

32:51.578 --> 32:54.755
There's resources on other
planets that can benefit us.

32:54.798 --> 32:56.757
It sounds crazy, I know.

32:56.800 --> 32:59.803
Which is why I haven't told you.

32:59.847 --> 33:01.109
Or anyone else.

33:01.153 --> 33:03.111
But other people are trying
to do this.

33:03.155 --> 33:05.200
It's not crazy.Yeah, but those people

33:05.244 --> 33:08.203
are the same three billionaires
that everyone knows.

33:08.247 --> 33:09.683
A Black billionaire doing this

33:09.726 --> 33:12.207
is a whole different
conversation.

33:12.251 --> 33:13.774
I just lost the one
scientist I needed

33:13.817 --> 33:15.602
to make this a reality.

33:15.645 --> 33:17.778
I mean,
our resources are limited.

33:17.821 --> 33:19.736
There's overpopulation,
there's...

33:19.780 --> 33:23.001
I'm on a high.
Don't bring me down.

33:23.044 --> 33:26.178
The problems are overwhelming,
I know,

33:26.221 --> 33:27.744
but I want to fix them.

33:27.788 --> 33:29.920
And the scientist doesn't like
your ideas?

33:29.964 --> 33:32.227
He doesn't know
about the rocket part.

33:32.271 --> 33:36.318
If he doesn't know your dream...

33:36.362 --> 33:38.016
